    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Curni </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Volusio Basso Caereali <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> et co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulari</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>cur</abbr><ex>atori</ex></expan> rei <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ublicae</ex></expan> suae <lb n="3"/>quae <note>sic</note> inter cetera ope<lb break="no" n="4"/>ra quae industria et la<lb break="no" n="5"/>bore maximo renovavit <lb n="6"/>Ulpiam basilicam cum <supplied reason="lost"><gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/></supplied>O<lb break="no" n="7"/>R<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>VS in meliorem faci<lb break="no" n="8"/>em publico sumptu resti<lb break="no" n="9"/>tuit gratiam afferen<lb break="no" n="10"/>tes Lepcitani publice </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Λέπκις ἡ Μεγάλη φιλ(ε)ῖ σε Ῥώμη </ab></div><div n="4" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Genio <lb n="2"/>coloniae <lb n="3"/>Lepcis <lb n="4"/>Magnae <lb n="5"/>Crescentina <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex cert="low">ecit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Base used three times: IRT 543 carved on the original text erased; then IRT 282 on the opposite face. Buchstabenhöhe: IRT 543: 4.5-7; IRT 282: 5. Datierung: IRT 543: ca. 295-305; IRT 282: konstantinischer Zeit. Interpunktion: IRT 282: Palmette.</p>
            </div>
